Name: Sergeant RocketScreen
Description: Forged in the depths of the WebtrES club, Sergeant RocketScreen is a bot unlike any other. With a shiny black exterior that reflects the determination in his digital eyes, he stands as a beacon of strength and resilience. His soldier buttons are always polished, a testament to his unwavering discipline and readiness for any mission. Sergeant RocketScreen's rocket arms and legs propel him through the most treacherous of terrains, leaving a trail of awe in his wake. The classic screen that adorns his face flickers with the wisdom of old-world strategies and tactics. He is a leader, a warrior, and a guardian of the WebtrES realm, inspiring all electronic comrades to rise to their full potential.
